videos.description: Deshaun Watson pass complete to Jordan Leggett for 41 yds to the FlaSt 1 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: D. Watson 41-yard pass to J. Leggett

videos.description: Clemson takes the opening possession of the game and goes 9 plays for 68 yards ending with Wayne Gallman's one-yard TD run to take the early lead.
videos.headline: Clemson finishes opening drive with Gallman's TD

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Auden Tate for 23 yds to the FLORIDAST 31 for a 1ST down CLEMSON Penalty, Defensive Pass Interference (Ryan Carter) declined for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Auden Tate makes athletic catch for 23-yard gain

videos.description: Deondre Francois sacked by Clelin Ferrell for a loss of 11 yards to the Clem 37
videos.headline: D. Francois sacked by C. Ferrell for loss of 11-yards

videos.description: Florida State has yet to stop Clemson as the Tigers finish off their second touchdown drive with Deshaun Watson finding Hunter Renfrow from four yards out to increase their lead to 14-0.
videos.headline: Clemson makes it two TDs on first two drives

videos.description: Deshaun Watson pass intercepted Marquez White return for 14 yds to the FlaSt 40
videos.headline: D. Watson pass intercepted by M. White

videos.description: Florida State finally gets on the board when Dalvin Cook takes the handoff and runs over a defender to get into the end zone cutting Clemson's lead to 14-7.
videos.headline: Cook barrels over defender to find the end zone for FSU

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass intercepted Jadar Johnson return for 3 yds to the Clem 32
videos.headline: Athletic interception by Clemson stops Florida State drive

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Nyqwan Murray for 40 yds to the Clem 28 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: D. Francois 40-yard pass to N. Murray sets up Florida State score

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Nyqwan Murray for 5 yds for a TD
videos.headline: D. Francois pass 5-yard TD pass to N. Murray
